    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, chop your <strong>parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Zest <strong>half </strong>your <strong>lemon[s]</strong> (try to grate lightly with a micro-plane or sharp box grater and avoid grating the white pith, as this is very bitter)</p>",
      "order": 5,
